headline: US Senate Democratic candidates visit Voters In Centre County PA
author: Jennifer Lewis-Hall
sentences: John Fetterman, Conor Lamb and Malcolm Kenyatta make a stop in Centre County recently as they seek the democratic nomination for United States Senate.
Reporter Jordan Tracy tells us about some of the top issues on minds of voters and how each candidate hopes to address it.
